EDI Document 865 - Purchase Order Change Acknowledgment
Function:
The EDI 865 Purchase Order Change Acknowledgment document is used to acknowledge receipt of and indicate acceptance or rejection of changes to a purchase order.

Example:

ISA*00*          *00*          *ZZ*SENDERID      *ZZ*RECEIVERID    *YYMMDD*HHMM*U*00501*000000001*0*P*>~
GS*PC*SENDERID*RECEIVERID*YYMMDD*HHMM*1*X*005010~
ST*865*0001~
BCT*00*ORIGINAL CONTROL NUMBER*20230701*HHMM*TRANSACTION TYPE*ORIGINAL REFERENCE NUMBER~
N1*BY*BUYER NAME*92*BUYERID~
N1*SU*SUPPLIER NAME*92*SUPPLIERID~
PO1*1*100*EA*UNIT PRICE**UP*PRODUCT CODE*VP*SKU12345~
PO1*2*200*EA*UNIT PRICE**UP*PRODUCT CODE*VP*SKU67890~
CTT*2*TOTAL LINE ITEMS~
SE*9*0001~
GE*1*1~
IEA*1*000000001~

Purpose in Lizgate Enterprise:
In Lizgate Enterprise, the EDI 865 document confirms receipt and acceptance of changes to purchase orders, ensuring alignment between buyer and supplier regarding order modifications.